      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOTS OF CHANGE (10) has been in the placings two times from as many runs this campaign. Registered yet another strong performance last start when he battled on bravely to just miss out over 2503m at Gloucester Park, adding to a string of recent minor placings. Meets a similar line up and he can take this out. THE HONOURS NZ (7) was out of the money two starts ago then things went amiss last start when he broke and finished a distant 11th over 2503m at Gloucester Park. Big chance if he behaves in this similar assignment. ELISH STAR (3) is a great chance after a string of sound recent performances, the latest a solid second at this track over 1684m. Hard to find fault. BEE BEE BEROC (4) was unplaced two starts ago then things went amiss last start when he broke and finished 12 metres away in fifth over 1684m at this track. Won't find this any harder and he can bounce back.",
